    "body": "@vvo \n\nFor NPM < 3 this causes two version of react to be loaded, and the app to go [kaboom](https://facebook.github.io/react/warnings/refs-must-have-owner.html). The guys at material-ui had a similar issue, [here](https://github.com/callemall/material-ui/issues/2818#issuecomment-170708363).\n",
